msgstr ""

#: ../../source/troubleshooting/fix_venvs.rst:172
msgid ""
"JupyterLab discovers environments through kernel specifications — small "
"JSON files that point to a specific Python binary. When you recreate an "
"environment, the old kernel specification still points to the broken "
"binary, so JupyterLab cannot find or use the new environment. You need to"
" remove the old specification and register a new one."
msgstr ""

